name: Rorschach Algorithmic Perceptions
description: Rorschach Algorithmic Perceptions was created using A.I Generative algorithms applied to my Graffiti illustrations to create my own Rorschach. In this case, the A.I takes the illustration and gives us two conflicting beliefs. This inconsistency between what is seen and believed is designed to motivate people to engage with the artwork. The music was also created using algorithms generated from the images and mixed with old style tape loops, as added atmosphere.
